                     <interp inst="t17730421-35-person463" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker: the prisoner pawned a waistcoat with me on the 18th of February; a muslin handkerchief on the 19th, a lawn apron on the 20th and a pair of stone buttons on the 25th; she said they were her own property.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17730421-35-person464">
