            . I am clerk to Mr. Cradon, a pawnbroker; four damask clouts, and a piece of new cloth were pawned at our house the beginning of March by the prisoner (producing them.)</p>
               <p>Mrs. Mills. I am certain these are the Prosecutor's property.</p>
               <p>- Yarday. I am a pawnbroker: the half shift was pawned with me on the 22nd of February, by the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I did it through necessity.</p>
